Teacher -> UI: Truy cập trang chấm bài Writing
activate UI

UI -> Controller: GET /api/writing/pending
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: getPendingSubmissions(teacherId)
activate Service

Service -> DB: SELECT * FROM student_writing_submission\nWHERE status = 'PENDING'\nAND graded_by_id IS NULL
activate DB
DB --> Service: List<WritingSubmission>
deactivate DB

Service --> Controller: List<WritingSubmission>
deactivate Service

Controller --> UI: 200 OK\n{submissions}
deactivate Controller

UI --> Teacher: Hiển thị danh sách bài Writing chờ chấm
deactivate UI

Teacher -> UI: Click vào một bài Writing
activate UI

UI -> Controller: GET /api/writing/submission/{submissionId}
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: getSubmissionDetail(submissionId)
activate Service

