activate DB
DB --> Service: WritingSubmission
deactivate DB

Service -> DB: SELECT * FROM question_group\nWHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> Service: QuestionGroup (đề bài)
deactivate DB

Service --> Controller: WritingSubmissionDetail
deactivate Service

Controller --> UI: 200 OK\n{submission, prompt, content}
